{OPENAGHMATHJAX()}{L=r\times p}{OPENAGHMATHJAX}. Zgodnie z drugą zasadą dynamiki Newtona {OPENAGHMATHJAX()}{\tau
=\frac{\mathit{dL}}{\mathit{dt}}}{OPENAGHMATHJAX}.}
